msgctxt "items.description"
msgid "I should learn to sew costumes sometime."
msgstr "Faudrait que j'apprenne à coudre des costumes un jour."

#. ID 35
msgctxt "items.name"
msgid "Eyeball"
msgstr "Globe oculaire"

#. ID 35
msgctxt "items.description"
msgid "Eww, and it's kind of big!"
msgstr "Ouww, et il est plutôt grand !"

#. ID 36
msgctxt "items.name"
msgid "Heart"
msgstr "Cœur"

#. ID 36
msgctxt "items.description"
msgid "Oh my God, that's a pumping human heart!"
msgstr "Oh mon Dieu, c'est un cœur humain qui bat encore !"

#. ID 37
msgctxt "items.name"
msgid "Guitar"
msgstr "Guitare"

#. ID 37
msgctxt "items.description"
msgid "Feldon said I could always borrow this..."
msgstr "Feldon a dit que je pouvais l'emprunter..."

#. ID 38
msgctxt "items.name"
msgid "Sketchbook"
msgstr "Carnet à croquis"

#. ID 38
msgctxt "items.description"
msgid "The drawings are a little... unsettling?"
msgstr "Les dessins sont un peu... perturbants ?"

#. ID 39
msgctxt "items.name"
msgid "Bloody Knife"
msgstr "Couteau ensanglanté"

#. ID 39
msgctxt "items.description"
msgid "But I didn't kill Martha!"
msgstr "Mais je n'ai pas tué Martha !"

#. ID 40
msgctxt "items.name"
msgid "Red Marker"
msgstr "Marqueur rouge"

#. ID 40
msgctxt "items.description"
msgid "I use this to draw bad feelings."
msgstr "Je l'utilise pour dessiner des mauvais sentiments."

#. ID 41
msgctxt "items.name"
msgid "Skull"
msgstr "Crâne"

#. ID 41
msgctxt "items.description"
msgid "Why am I carrying this!?"
msgstr "Pourquoi est-ce que je transporte ça !?"

#. ID 42
msgctxt "items.name"
msgid "Wart"
msgstr "Verrue"

#. ID 42
msgctxt "items.description"
msgid "It's sticky, and an eye is coming out of it!"
msgstr "Ça colle, et un œil en sort !"

#. ID 43
msgctxt "items.name"
msgid "Martha's Voice"
msgstr "Voix de Martha"

#. ID 43
msgctxt "items.description"
msgid "Why? Get it out! Get it out!"
msgstr "Pourquoi ? Sort de là ! Sort de là !"

#. ID 44
msgctxt "items.name"
msgid "Dream Diary"
msgstr "Journal des rêves"

#. ID 44
msgctxt "items.description"
msgid "My old dream journal! Let's keep it shut forever."
msgstr "Mon vieux journal des rêves ! Gardons-le fermé."

#. ID 45
msgctxt "items.name"
msgid "Fidget Spinner"
msgstr "Hand spinner"

#. ID 45
msgctxt "items.description"
msgid "I think one of my friends would like this."
msgstr "Je pense qu'un de mes amis aimerait ça."

